"index_reference": "4633",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A beast of burden, used to carry both goods and people.</p>\n<h2>Used for carrying goods</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:20\">1SA 16:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:3-Gen22:5\">GEN 22:3–22:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:27\">GEN 42:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:12\">EXO 23:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:14\">DEU 5:14</a> <em>As beasts of burden they were afforded rest on the Sabbath.</em></p>\n<h2>Used for personal transport</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:20\">1SA 25:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:7\">MAT 21:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:20\">EXO 4:20</a>NUM <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22\">22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:16\">2PE 2:16</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh15:18\">JOS 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:28\">JDG 19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:23\">2SA 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:26\">2SA 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:23-1Kgs13:29\">1KI 13:23–13:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:34\">LUK 10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:14\">JHN 12:14</a></p>\n<h2>The value of donkeys</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:4\">EXO 22:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:21\">DEU 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:9\">EXO 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:15\">NUM 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:3-Deut22:4\">DEU 22:3–22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:3\">1SA 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:3\">JOB 24:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:15\">LUK 13:15</a></p>\n<h2>Mistreatment of donkeys</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:23\">NUM 22:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:10\">DEU 22:10</a></p>\n<h2>Sometimes found in the wild</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:5\">JOB 39:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:5\">JOB 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:24\">JER 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:9\">HOS 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of the donkey</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:12\">GEN 16:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:14\">GEN 49:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:3\">ISA 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:19\">JER 22:19</a></p>\n<h2>Samson and the donkey's jaw-bone</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:15-Judg15:16\">JDG 15:15–15:16</a></p>",
